ZH: 我今天早上喝了一杯热饮料。
EN: I drank a hot beverage this morning.

ZH: 你想要什么样的饮料？
EN: What kind of beverage would you like?

ZH: 我每天都喜欢喝凉爽的饮料。
EN: I enjoy drinking cold beverages every day.

ZH: 我最喜欢的饮料是奶茶。
EN: My favorite beverage is milk tea.

ZH: 他喜欢喝有咖啡因的饮料。
EN: He likes to drink caffeinated beverages.

ZH: 健康饮料对我们的身体很重要。
EN: Healthy beverages are important for our bodies.

ZH: 请给我来杯热的饮料。
EN: Please give me a hot beverage.

ZH: 饮料可以帮助我们保持清醒。
EN: Beverages can help us stay alert.

ZH: 这家餐厅提供各种不同种类的饮料。
EN: This restaurant offers a variety of different beverages.

ZH: 饮料可以解渴。
EN: Beverages can quench thirst.

ZH: 我们应该减少饮料中的糖分。
EN: We should reduce the sugar content in beverages.

ZH: 他习惯在早晨喝一杯果汁等饮料。
EN: He is used to drinking juice and other beverages in the morning.

ZH: 饮料的种类非常多。
EN: There are many different kinds of beverages.

ZH: 请随便选择一种饮料。
EN: Please feel free to choose a beverage.

ZH: 饮料应该适量摄入。
EN: Beverages should be consumed in moderation.

ZH: 我很喜欢这个新品牌的饮料。
EN: I really like this new brand of beverage.

ZH: 他们对这种饮料有着浓厚的兴趣。
EN: They have a strong interest in this type of beverage.

ZH: 请不要忘记给客人提供饮料。
EN: Don't forget to offer beverages to the guests.

ZH: 很多人在早餐时会喝咖啡或茶等热饮料。
EN: Many people drink coffee or tea as hot beverages during breakfast.

ZH: 他们在夏天最喜欢喝冰镇的饮料。
EN: They love drinking chilled beverages the most in summer.
